Type Parameters:.K: the type of keys maintained by this map.

Methods.clear(): removes all of the mappings from this map.
Methods.containsKey(Object key): returns true if this map contains key.
Methods.containsValue(Object value): returns true if this map contains value.
Methods.entrySet(): returns a Set view of the mappings contained in this map.
Methods.forEach(BiConsumer<? super K, ? super V>: performs the given action for each entry in this map until all entries have been processed.
Methods.isEmpty(): returns true if this map contains no key-value mappings.
Methods.keySet(): returns a Set view of the keys contained in this map.
Methods.put(K key, V value): add the key, value pair to this map.
Methods.replace(K key, V value): replace the current value of key with value.
Methods.size(): returns the number of key-value mappings in this map.
Methods.values: return a collection view of the values contained in this map.
